CHAT.comment: Lunch. Mother sits feeding Child noodle soup. Child is in a high chair in the kitchen. Child quite unintelligible.

u.a: gaze camera and feeds self with empty spoon .
pushes noodles in mouth with fingers .
drops some noodles in her lap .
eats noodles off high chair tray .
reaches for spoon then sits back .
pushes noodles in mouth with hand .
uses spoon to wipe Child's mouth .
tries to pull away too soon .
bounces to radio music , points to radio .
reaches for spoon then sits back .
feeds self and gets noodles on face .
takes spoon , won't give it back .
